quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  28,12,"Men harminani mo ko adii, (en…ói) muynir…ói …óin, (banndiraawo makko on) wi'i: \"On accay mi tinndinay on fii yim…ďe suudu, …ďe ne'ana on mo, hara kadi ko laa…ďanay …ďe mo"
  28,13,"Men rutti mo ka yumma makko, fii yo …ďernde makko …ďuu…ďu, hara o sunaaki, e fii yo o anndu pellet, fodoore Alla nden, ko goonga. Kono …ďur…ďe …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe anndaa"
  28,14,"Nde o yottinoo sagatalaaku makko ngun, o fotondi- ri, Men okki mo faamu e ganndal. Ko wano non Men yo…ďirta mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďen"
  28,15,"O naatiri e saare nden, fewndo welsindaare yim…ďe mayre; o tawi wor…ďe …ói…óo no ha…ďa ton: go…ó…óo on ko jeyaa…óo e le√Īol makko, oya on ko jeyaa…óo e ay…ďe makko …ďen. Jeyaa…óo e le√Īol makko ngol …óa…ď…ďiri faabo e hoore jeyaa…óo e ga√Īo makko on. Muusaa uttii mo, nde gayni fii makko. [Muusaa] maaki: \"∆äum …óoo, ko jeyaa…óum e kuu…óe seytaane. Pellet, ko o ga√Īo, majjinoowo …ďanngu…óo"
  28,16,"O maaki: \"Joomi am, mi too√Īii hoore-am; haforanam.\" O haforani mo. Pellet, ko Kanko woni Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo On"
  28,17,"O maaki: \"Joomi am, sabu ko neemin…óaa kon e am, mi wontataa ballo bom…ďe …ďen"
  28,18,"O wonti hul…óo ka saare, himo habbii [nanngeede]. Tawi faabinornoo…óo mo on hanki, hino faabinora mo [hannde kadi]. Muusaa maakani mo: \"Pellet, ko a bew…óo …ďanngu…óo"
  28,19,"Nde Muusaa faandinoo nanngugol taw…óo on ko ga√Īo ma…ď…ďe kam…ďe …ói…óo, o wi'i: \"Ko an yo Muusaa, a faala warugol lam, wano ittirno…óaa wonkii non hanki? A faandaaki, si wanaa wonugol dunndarankeejo ka leydi, a faandaaki jeyeede e mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďen"
  28,20,"Gorko iwri ka …ďuri wo…ó…óude e saare nden, himo yaccoo, o wi'i: \"Ko an yo Muusaa, mbatu ngun no fewjana fii warugol maa. Yaltu (e leydi ndin). Ko mi jeyaa…óo e laa…ďanoo…ďe ma"
  28,21,"O yalti ton, ko o hulu…óo, himo tijjii [nanngeede]. O maaki: \"Joomi am, dan…óndam e yim…ďe too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  28,22,"Nde o fewtunoo hella Madyana, o maaki: \"Hino hasii ka Joomi am fewnirta lam, e laawol focciingol ngol"
  28,23,"Nde o hewtunoo ka …ďunndu Madyana, o tawi …óon dental yim…ďe, hi…ďe yarna [daabeeji ma…ď…ďe], o tawi gaanin ma…ď…ďe, rew…ďe …ói…óo, no sogga [dammi ma…ď…ďe], o maaki: \"Ko hon…óum habbi-…óon?\" ∆Āe wi'i: \"Men yarnataa haa aynoo…ďe …ďen deestoo, baaba amen, ko maw…óo nayeejo"
  28,24,"O yarnani …ďe [dammi …óin], refti o huccitiri ka …óowdi, o maaki: \"Joomi am, min ko jippin…óaa e am woo e mo∆ī∆īere, ko mi hatonji…óo"
  28,25,"Gooto e [jiw…ďe] …ďen ari e makko, himo yahra hersa, o wi'i: \"Baaba am no nodde, fii yo o yo…ďe njo…ďdi kon ko yarnan-…óaa men\". Tuma o hewtunoo ka [maw…óo] on, o sifanii mo fii [makko], o maaki: \"Wata a hulu, a da…óii yim…ďe too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  28,26,"Gooto e [jiw…ďe] …ďen wi'i: \"∆≥ettu mo golle, yo baaba. Pellet, ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e mo ∆īettataa golle, ko doolnu…óo hoolnii…óo"
  28,27,"[Maw…óo] on maaki: \"Mi…óo yi…ói resingol ma gooto e jiw…ďe am …ďen …óoo …ói…óo, e hoore yo a golla-nam duu…ďi jeetati. Si a timminii sappo, haray ko e sago maa; mi faalaaka sa…ótinannde ma. A taway lam, si Alla ja…ďii, ko e mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďen mi jeyaa"
  28,28,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"∆äum wonii hakkunde am e mon. Happu woo e majji …ói…ói, …ói mi hunni, haray …ďi…óteede alanaa e lam. En wa…óii Alla fawtii…óo e ko wowlu…óen kon"